        <mxCell id="f9-note1" value="EXTRACTION PATTERN:&#xa;To extract any engine as standalone SaaS:&#xa;1. Copy engine's API routes, workers, and tables&#xa;2. Replace Event Bus subscriptions with REST webhook endpoints&#xa;3. Replace Event Bus publishes with webhook callouts&#xa;4. Inject shared infra (DB, Redis, AI) via config&#xa;5. Deploy independently — zero code changes to other engines" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;size=14;fillColor=#FFFDE7;strokeColor=#999;fontSize=10;fontStyle=0;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
